l: Judges
l: Ruth
l: The First Book of Samuel
l: The Second Book of Samuel
l: The First Book of Kings
l: The Second Book of Kings
l: The First Book of Chronicles
l: The Second Book of Chronicles
l: The First Book of Esdras
l: The Second Book of Esdras
